==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Knobbed
<hw>Knobbed</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Containing knobs; full
of knobs; ending in a nob. See <xex>Illust</xex> of
<er>Antenna</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The horns of a roe deer of Greenland are pointed at the top, and
<qex>knobbed</qex> or tuberous at the bottom.</q>
<rj><qau>Grew.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Knobber</ent>⟦br⟧
